To install the xtheme program suite, simply run

sh INSTALL.sh [ options ]

options:
	-a	do not prompt for questions
	-d dir	install to/remove from dir
	-r	remove
	-u	update
	-y	synonym for -a

You will be prompted for where to install it.
You may be prompted for locations of missing programs.
Failure to provide those locations will result in termination.

(...of the program! What were YOU thinking?)
